name: exodus - cover page
description:
✣ watercolour, nankim and grafite on 300g/m² cotton paper | 7200x5100px ✣ franxyk.tumblr.com

exodus is an experimental comic zine I started to make on 2020 and finished on the late 2021. Exodus is a world that means travel, movement, intection and this journey is a exodus to inside. To see inside, to meet yourself, a great intention of being with yourself.

When I beggining to make it, covid-19 pandemic isolation was about so start and i had to left where I live to live with my parents because I was without money and then I was with no friend just my parents and the only option I saw was to be with myself I was never being. So that is what is about. 

This is the cover from this comic zine I made and if you're to buy it just contact me frfolle@gmail.com I can send you wherever you are. Or if you're in Brazil use this to buy: xyk.minestore.com.br 

Thxxx <3
